welp its official I have the Flu! grr.. I've been feelin like shit all week and I just got back from the doctors and he said I have the Flu.. updates:

Monday: got up at 4:30 for hockey practice.. worked my butt off cause the sickness was setting in and i didnt feel good.. then after practice went to school to shower and get ready for school.. while i was in the shower i heard mrs. murphy come over the announcements but i wasnt quite sure if i heard right.. something about school being cancelled and all the girls in the locker room started screaming and freaking out.. when I got out of the shower I asked what was going on school was cancelled whoop whoop! a pipe burst or something! so we got showered and dressed then Sarah drove me, Spaz, & Amanda out to breakfast with Charlotte.. we went to Newport Creamy near LSA but madd LSA people we already there and we didnt feel like waiting so we went to Friendlys instead.. we just all chylled and were bein stupid.. then when I got home chylled out for a while and what not.. then Bri came over cause she had the car and her and I drove around for a while being stupid.. then me and my sis went to the mall.. fun filled day.. but we hada take ripta home and being out in the cold didnt help at all! 

Tuesday: didn't feel good at all I tossed and turned all night long and I had like the sweats and the chylls I was flippin out! I was hacking my brains out coughin so much. wicked stuffy nose and what not. And just my whole entire body hurt. I don't cry when I'm sick but I was sittin there crying because no matter what i did.. stand.. sit.. lay down.. it was like I was putting pressure on my body and it hurt. I attempted to sleep all day but it didnt work i was awake.. sleeping.. awake.. sleeping.. and i didnt eat at all the thought of food was making me sick! and once I was finally awake enough to talk I called Nate because I had felt bad that he wanted me to cover for him because he didnt know I was sick and probably thought I was being a huge bitch because he covers for me all the time. So I called him and explained then he felt bad he kept calling me so many times monday night trying to see if I would.. he called my house a buncha times and my cell.. then over night he called 7 times can you tell he really didnt want to work? but he ended up calling out sick and someone else took over.. so I was glad because I felt bad!
Today: got up at 4:30 for hockey practice I went but I didnt practice I was waayy to sick.. and coach bob said he didnt want me getting sicker by playing tonight at the game so I had to rest and he was playing me in Saturdays game.. so I chylled out all day sleeping and what not.. then my mom was going to take me to a walk in to get checked out then take me over to Spaz's so her dad could take me to the game so I could at least watch.. but the walk in doesnt take our insurance anymore.. I guess it doesnt take Blue cross blue chip or something so my mom made a doctors appointment for me for 5:15.. she was going to drop me off at the game after but when the doctor said I have the Flu and he cant put me on any meds my mom said I have to stay home tonight.. grr! I just felt really bad because I wanted to go and support my team plus it's Spaz's first game she played in and I missed it! but what can I do I feel like SHIT.. arg.. but at least because of the plumbing problems at school we havent had school.. they are reopening tomorrow weather permitting but I'm not going either way so I hope it gets cancelled so I don't miss! I want to stay out Friday too but if I do then I can't play in the game Saturday (stupid school rule!) I'm really whiped out so I'm going to go.. I have some pics to post but Ill probably do it tomorrow or something cause I'm guna pass out.. xO
